---
import CampaignLayout from '../../layouts/CampaignLayout.astro';
---

<CampaignLayout
  title="Free Bystander Intervention Training | Level Up"
  description="Join Level Up's free online bystander intervention training and learn how to safely interrupt harassment in public, at work, in your family or in your community."
  heroImage="https://welevelup.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/we-protect-us-2.webp"
  heroTitle="Free Bystander Intervention Training"
  heroSubtitle="we protect us"
>

  <h1 class="campaign-main-title">Free Bystander Intervention Training</h1>
  <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 400; text-align: center; color: #0D0A3E; margin-bottom: 1rem;">we protect us</h2>
  <p class="campaign-main-description">Join Level Up's free online bystander intervention training and learn how to safely interrupt harassment in public, at work, in your family or in your community.</p>
  <p class="campaign-main-description">We provide practical, feminist-led training sessions that equip you with the skills to intervene in cases of sexist, racist, LGBTQ+ or Islamophobic harassment and gender-based violence.</p>

  <div style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0;">
    <a href="https://levelup.yourmovement.org/p/we-protect-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="campaign-btn">SIGN UP FOR TRAININGS</a>
  </div>

  <div class="campaign-section">
    <div class="campaign-section__label">
      <h2>What the training is</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="campaign-section__text">
      <p>The fight for gender justice takes real action on a daily basis, but sometimes it's hard to know what that looks like.</p>
      <p>That's why Level Up runs free online bystander intervention sessions – to give everyone the skills they need to intervene when they see harassment happening.</p>
      <p>In the past year, we've trained 413 people, and we're running more sessions!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="campaign-section">
    <div class="campaign-section__label">
      <h2>Why we run it</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="campaign-section__text">
      <p>Violence in our society – from sexist or racist harassment and domestic abuse to LGBTQ+ or Islamophobic hate crime – will not be prevented through more policing. It will only be prevented if we all take action. We protect us, we keep each other safe.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="campaign-section">
    <div class="campaign-section__label">
      <h2>Next Event</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="campaign-section__text">
      <p>Subscribe to our mailing list to stay updated on upcoming training sessions.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <a href="https://levelup.yourmovement.org/p/we-protect-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="campaign-btn">SIGN UP FOR TRAININGS</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="campaign-section">
    <div class="campaign-section__label">
      <h2>Bystander Intervention in Action</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="campaign-section__text">
      <p>Level Up and Black Protest Legal Support created a short video featuring Sapphire Mackintosh on using your agency to intervene in a police stop and search.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0;">
    <a href="https://levelup.yourmovement.org/p/join-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="campaign-btn">Join the Level Up Community</a>
  </div>

</CampaignLayout>
